extendedInfo.description: Dominoes comes to Android!Ahora soporta espaÃ±ol.This version is known as Straight Dominoes, Fives Up, All Fives, or Muggins. Take turns against the computer opponent. Score when the ends add up to a multiple of 5. Play to a score of 250.Classic fun for all ages!

reviews.title: Never win
reviews.comment: I would give this game a 4 are 5 but the fact then when u play the computer it seems to always have points are the right bones to lock u out are score I played a total of 40 games and I won less then 10 and I\'m a good bone player just seems it\'s made for the human player to loose even if u have a Big lead
reviews.author: Kendrick Brockington

reviews.title: Excellent
reviews.comment: This version is excellent. I can\'t imagine needing anything more in a dominoes game. So wierd i win at least 75pct of the games,  don\'t listen to the ppl who can\'t win...  Lol!
reviews.author: Ed Williams

reviews.title: Decent
reviews.comment: Don\'t listen to the lies. The CPU is good but only because it\'s a computer. The games are winnable and is a good representation of domino
reviews.author: Tyler Wintringham

reviews.title: Dominoes
reviews.comment: Opponent always has a better hand, even when I get a great hand, he always has just enough to keep me cut off and doubles sometimes turn wrong.  It is still the best domino game \"avalible\". I still recomend this app. but only b/c all the others are so poor.
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: NOTHING FIXED!!
reviews.comment: STILL HAS TERRIBLE GLITCHES. IT REVERSES DOMINOS WHEN PLAYED. ABSOLUTELY HORRIBLE. IT ALSO MISSES POINTS.  MAYBE THE MAKERS DON\'T GIVE A CRAP ABOUT UPDATING AND FIXING THEIR PRODUCT. DON\'T WASTE YOUR MONEY UNTIL THEY UPDATE.
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: Was good.
reviews.comment: Starting to have glitches.  Tiles not connecting but game still in play.  Annoying.  Seems like it would be easy to fix, being a developer & all.

reviews.title: Don\'t waste your time
reviews.comment: The game cheats. Constantly.  For example: The AI will drop the double five, then I put down the five blank, and the AI will use the double blank EVERY SINGLE TIME. Also, very glitchy. Dominos will randomly get placed off the normal pattern, which becomes confusing. Waste of money.
